{"tid":89461,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"同ex分開將近十年，好感激當初遇到佢","createTime":"2017-01-21T10:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-22T16:44:46.000Z","uid":26320,"like":90,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"5fa7226837243807e15b0ac06ae90cdcbfb985d3","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T10:56:04.000Z","msg":"同ex拍咗4年，忍痛嗌分手。<br />\n但太痛苦，好蠢咁聽人講開始一段新戀情就可以忘記。<br />\n<br />\n所以同咗一個男仔拍拖一年，嘗試去接受佢，試去愛佢，試去投入嚟段感情，而個腦不斷出現嘅係ex，啲回憶會侵襲你，佢明知我個心有ex，佢都無同我分手，繼續對我好好，最後拖咗一年就分咗手。<br />\n<br />\n後來覺得唔想再傷害人，都唔想再不斷折磨自己，決定好要放低ex再去重新出發，去搵個好愛嘅先再拍拖，所以再用咗一年時間由痛苦去到放下，真係要多謝班朋友成日帶我出去户外活動等我放鬆，去感受生命中有嘅嘢唔係得ex。<br />\n<br />\n最後，係有一日收到ex媽咪嘅一個邀請，邀請我去ex哥哥個女嘅百日宴，我去咗因為想睇下嚟一年嘅成果有無效，的確係有效，我再見到佢已經無心動or心痛嘅感覺，重要諗點解當初會鍾意嚟個花心男。<br />\n亦都係當日嘅宴會裹面認識到同枱嘅男生，同佢拍拖將近四年，係嚟將近四年裹面，我覺得非常幸福。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n多謝ex令我知道，佢當初有幾咁仆街，令我更珍惜現任。唔係ex，我唔會知道原來比人愛唔係必然，比人愛唔應該每日以淚洗面，愛人原來係會覺得幸福，愛人係每日都好開心。"},{"pid":"bd499f952ca5297b7fdd59a853186ef5176cccc8","tid":89461,"uid":68589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:22:20.000Z","msg":"正能量<br />\n做好自己, 生活好, 改善人際關係, 愛情會降臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"082856e78442847452a8d47dbd7a65d4a5a06106","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T11:57:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正能量<br />\n做好自己, 生活好, 改善人際關係, 愛情會降臨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n希望你都可以放低，重新出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c52e77ae4f7d381a33e25ba9f0933493346be7f6","tid":89461,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:02:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都要努力放低"},{"pid":"ef46596cdba52302f9b98b7fa097abd5976df58c","tid":89461,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:18:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都很感謝我的ex<br />\n在我生命最燦爛，<br />\n最無助的時候你不離不棄在我身邊<br />\n<br />\n一直以來你總是帶領著我成長<br />\n後來我知道你累了<br />\n我也沒有挽留<br />\n<br />\n我會學著放棄你<br />\n是因為我太愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第13年"},{"pid":"ca1667546ed4d69cf96d17cd4873df54282f129a","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:28:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我都要努力放低</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n加油啊，唔好迫自己去放低，去嘗試就得。過分在意去放低反而會更上心。"},{"pid":"1e87992c5f3544653c4c2ae713f44a667c4a0666","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:29:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都很感謝我的ex<br />\n在我生命最燦爛，<br />\n最無助的時候你不離不棄在我身邊<br />\n<br />\n一直以來你總是帶領著我成長<br />\n後來我知道你累了<br />\n我也沒有挽留<br />\n<br />\n我會學著放棄你<br />\n是因為我太愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第13年</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你係分咗手第十三年定一齊咗第十三年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f9622d8585d60625687884351a695404af2ef6d","tid":89461,"uid":64944,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:39:13.000Z","msg":"咁你好彩，之後遇到個好人<br />\n好多人遇人不淑係接二連三，鑊鑊識親都係仆街"},{"pid":"448111f8dc27b6455ad1029ea4139518c11e64f7","tid":89461,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:41:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都很感謝我的ex<br />\n在我生命最燦爛，<br />\n最無助的時候你不離不棄在我身邊<br />\n<br />\n一直以來你總是帶領著我成長<br />\n後來我知道你累了<br />\n我也沒有挽留<br />\n<br />\n我會學著放棄你<br />\n是因為我太愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第13年</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 04拍拖10分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2ec8e5b92e9d9c5a04950332bc39dfdf2ec768","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:45:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁你好彩，之後遇到個好人<br />\n好多人遇人不淑係接二連三，鑊鑊識親都係仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確係幾好彩嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果我識親都係仆街，我應該都會幾傷感，諗吓自己到底有乜吸引仆街嘅能力，係優點都會改咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"852a47842d2f7cbcacf9c1459c16aef012771157","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:48:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都很感謝我的ex<br />\n在我生命最燦爛，<br />\n最無助的時候你不離不棄在我身邊<br />\n<br />\n一直以來你總是帶領著我成長<br />\n後來我知道你累了<br />\n我也沒有挽留<br />\n<br />\n我會學著放棄你<br />\n是因為我太愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第13年</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 04拍拖10分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁多年，都重未放低？唔係長情咁簡單，係痴情啦啵。 有無出去行走吓啊？"},{"pid":"42a43708bd1db09c881c660b9e5ab08a760a4823","tid":89461,"uid":18739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:54:16.000Z","msg":"成功轉化&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b41004481fd74c867d7c96728f01b73ff30a175","tid":89461,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:55:48.000Z","msg":"水泡男真陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a7bae5d5129ccef9962b68b2974be486418412c","tid":89461,"uid":11381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"好dramatic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝你幸福"},{"pid":"4f5f00b390f20685b34475c646e62c506a0bd951","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:22:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>水泡男真陰功<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我都覺得好對佢唔住，有次同現任係車見到佢尷尬到不得之了，好想同佢道歉當年對佢嘅傷害，但我見佢睥實我，我知道道歉都無辦法彌補過去。<br />\n所以見到朋友想搵水泡時我都會同朋友講我做錯嘅事，希望大家唔好好似我咁錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係會良心責備自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dc2f1fc44176a92a9e0845a8046605c04101b385","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:24:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好dramatic<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n祝你幸福</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人生滿希望啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n多謝你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91fc7be3e3a3e8b648144f9a77e2fc419f44f62","tid":89461,"uid":22243,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:37:44.000Z","msg":"正能量，比個like你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cce256a891484d510d790f8ad5f7f12bbcc54a3d","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T15:42:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>正能量，比個like你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.