core":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T18:27:21.000Z","msg":"係百日宴識到個同枱既男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ......"},{"pid":"d92e309565cf4df7e9074d3b8301e89e2988b494","tid":89461,"uid":58005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T22:49:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你怪人時有無諗過，水泡男其實都諗點解識到個咁仆街既女仔</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n利申：中過伏，好撚 hurt"},{"pid":"8b5c779483a55f1811cb3125c8880876c6a20f42","tid":89461,"uid":15703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T22:55:53.000Z","msg":"最慘唔係你 係中間個男仔"},{"pid":"d4bfe80c4a60e4962ca7fdfc3a164736074653ad","tid":89461,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T23:48:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我都很感謝我的ex<br />\n在我生命最燦爛，<br />\n最無助的時候你不離不棄在我身邊<br />\n<br />\n一直以來你總是帶領著我成長<br />\n後來我知道你累了<br />\n我也沒有挽留<br />\n<br />\n我會學著放棄你<br />\n是因為我太愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n第13年</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 04拍拖10分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁多年，都重未放低？唔係長情咁簡單，係痴情啦啵。 有無出去行走吓啊？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開頭幾年都係一個人出去旅行散心<br />\n，相信我，一個人真係sad到爆<br />\n所以後來寧願唔出去"},{"pid":"3330a873bd1a2a76432d0b8b53433dbace5fb745","tid":89461,"uid":64691,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T23:51:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最慘唔係你 係中間個男仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢被遺忘到ex都稱唔上<br />\n<br />\nbtw我都係ex中間果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97a8ca4625e6c4a88c5a7f8c1b9780fb4be9bb8c","tid":89461,"uid":47309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-21T23:55:01.000Z","msg":"本來篇文我以為係講個水泡<br />\n點知直頭係無視人地<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5ce9488679b0384fc896f3dbc090712c84f494","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:33:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好男人是用來幫人埋單的</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現任計我之前，有9個前女朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可唔可以係互相埋單<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2e5d029e7a10ef74db98a91b72d922250b0aa551","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:34:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>絲打前男友係咪好撚靚仔?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n一啲都唔靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48581523340725403d15c25273c613aaf4315561","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:34:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>祝福你地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n多謝<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0126ad9abee62ee49c49ccb95ed26c8400600884","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:38:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁你好彩，之後遇到個好人<br />\n好多人遇人不淑係接二連三，鑊鑊識親都係仆街</blockquote><br />\n嗰啲叫 仆街攝石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我努力改變梗自己 希望唔好再吸仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家都有拍拖 希望可以好似樓主咁幸幸福福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 希望你幸福，加油！"},{"pid":"5e9dd318f5d88d75b9c7723caa245ec22a1ccefd","tid":89461,"uid":56084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:50:44.000Z","msg":"可唔可以講多d同現任既故事 有興趣知（例如點識，點發展，而家關係等等）"},{"pid":"b0d99830ac037d7ac745b3b4247ffe5d0cb53407","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:52:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你怪人時有無諗過，水泡男其實都諗點解識到個咁仆街既女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好多謝佢喎，唔係佢，我唔知自己有乜唔好，可以去改進。唔係佢，我唔會識到現任。<br />\n<br />\n而被大家稱呼為水泡男嘅，我只能講係我錯，當初真係相信可以愛上佢，我好努力投入嚟段感情，但勉強真係做唔到，我有諗過我欠佢嘅，同佢行埋嚟下半世人都好應該，但我日日對住佢就諗住另一個真係好過分，所以去到差唔多半年嘅時候已經叫分手。<br />\n<br />\n但多次叫分手而佢挽留我話唔介意做水泡，我又無拒絕佢真係好錯，所以係最後我無理佢一個月唔再依賴佢，先至正式分手。<br />\n<br />\n希望佢唔好再咁傻，都唔好再遇到咁仆街嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b65a7e8503bd47a2f7c88bd2512e3ca0b36c6f26","tid":89461,"uid":25516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:52:56.000Z","msg":"垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"813653424c0a7a31c7c9397f8f88439896005d25","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你怪人時有無諗過，水泡男其實都諗點解識到個咁仆街既女仔</blockquote><br />\nAgger<br />\n利申：中過伏，好撚 hurt</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n對唔住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5662b45969f2e5e841c0f6d375d40b6198e17e9","tid":89461,"uid":20419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:55:23.000Z","msg":"遇到花心男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我未花過心 對女朋友從不花心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17c14807643b19ef1043479ba58ab23d3347bed8","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:55:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最慘唔係你 係中間個男仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我一啲都唔慘，我都覺佢遇到我係最慘"},{"pid":"89a41887a7e7f8b189265e017d19e3c6bfa5966f","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:58:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 04拍拖10分手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n咁多年，都重未放低？唔係長情咁簡單，係痴情啦啵。 有無出去行走吓啊？</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 開頭幾年都係一個人出去旅行散心<br />\n，相信我，一個人真係sad到爆<br />\n所以後來寧願唔出去</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n要同朋友出去，我之前都係多得朋友見我唔出門自己係屋企亂諗嘢，所以帶我出去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 佢地真係好好"},{"pid":"54788368ff3aff29de36fcc0ed4442e6d6bd8274","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T04:59:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>最慘唔係你 係中間個男仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢被遺忘到ex都稱唔上<br />\n<br />\nbtw我都係ex中間果個<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 本來想打ex，但2個ex，好亂，同最主要想講頭果個ex。"},{"pid":"bc42c4bafde54291e8a13dbe9d6c7f2406f200b9","tid":89461,"uid":58005,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:05:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你怪人時有無諗過，水泡男其實都諗點解識到個咁仆街既女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好多謝佢喎，唔係佢，我唔知自己有乜唔好，可以去改進。唔係佢，我唔會識到現任。<br />\n<br />\n而被大家稱呼為水泡男嘅，我只能講係我錯，當初真係相信可以愛上佢，我好努力投入嚟段感情，但勉強真係做唔到，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我有諗過我欠佢嘅，同佢行埋嚟下半世人都好應該</span></span>，但我日日對住佢就諗住另一個真係好過分，所以去到差唔多半年嘅時候已經叫分手。<br />\n<br />\n但多次叫分手而佢挽留我話唔介意做水泡，我又無拒絕佢真係好錯，所以係最後我無理佢一個月唔再依賴佢，先至正式分手。<br />\n<br />\n希望佢唔好再咁傻，都唔好再遇到咁仆街嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，講到自己咁偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死仆街，一早應該放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3854eea876ad0f30b2913a0ab129f44aa945be2f","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:12:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>可唔可以講多d同現任既故事 有興趣知（例如點識，點發展，而家關係等等）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現任一開頭都講係百日宴同枱嘅男仔，見佢好幾傾，咪拎佢電話，當交個朋友。<br />\n真係鍾意其實係後來出嚟食嘢，一開始都無乜希望，佢幾多人追，幾好樣，而自己個陣滿面暗瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但約親都會即出，whatsapp又即應，"},{"pid":"4a19e050470a53ae92abbe6e95f52e3336e923d4","tid":89461,"uid":21331,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:15:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7507e656969f04c9f45e89c7f946dea910d33cab","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:16:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>可唔可以講多d同現任既故事 有興趣知（例如點識，點發展，而家關係等等）</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n現任一開頭都講係百日宴同枱嘅男仔，見佢好幾傾，咪拎佢電話，當交個朋友。<br />\n真係鍾意其實係後來出嚟食嘢，一開始都無乜希望，佢幾多人追，幾好樣，而自己個陣滿面暗瘡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但約親都會即出，whatsapp又即應，</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n未打曬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n覺得有啲機，咪表白一齊咯。<br />\n其實都係一齊之後先發現佢脾氣好臭嘅，一開頭都凈忍佢，後來佢知道我好唔開心，就一直改落去，到而家都好好仔。<br />\n無乜特別，我好鍾意我地嘅平淡，我地認定咗對方係另一半。"},{"pid":"9d0fa606d714de46fdaa8c212bf39a49c8457ddc","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:21:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你怪人時有無諗過，水泡男其實都諗點解識到個咁仆街既女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好多謝佢喎，唔係佢，我唔知自己有乜唔好，可以去改進。唔係佢，我唔會識到現任。<br />\n<br />\n而被大家稱呼為水泡男嘅，我只能講係我錯，當初真係相信可以愛上佢，我好努力投入嚟段感情，但勉強真係做唔到，<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我有諗過我欠佢嘅，同佢行埋嚟下半世人都好應該</span></span>，但我日日對住佢就諗住另一個真係好過分，所以去到差唔多半年嘅時候已經叫分手。<br />\n<br />\n但多次叫分手而佢挽留我話唔介意做水泡，我又無拒絕佢真係好錯，所以係最後我無理佢一個月唔再依賴佢，先至正式分手。<br />\n<br />\n希望佢唔好再咁傻，都唔好再遇到咁仆街嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屌你老母，講到自己咁偉大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n死仆街，一早應該放手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n嚟個唔係偉大嘅行為<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔知你點解會誤認為我係偉大，我覺得係好賤格嘅行為，為咗唔想欠佢，就同佢一直一齊唔去面對自己嘅錯，係好撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n你鬧我，我唔會拒絕，我都承認係我唔啱，我認為係我人生最錯嘅事，但無辦法去改變歷史<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 鬧我啦鬧我啦"},{"pid":"07585339d1ef2bb6d50f77cecb9bc3c2e4e43806","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:23:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>遇到花心男人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好彩我未花過心 對女朋友從不花心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n唔花心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最欣賞人唔花心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54fc19ce1d3d5cdbcc614a4ab85ff1de9e52b8d6","tid":89461,"uid":30710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:25:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>咁你好彩，之後遇到個好人<br />\n好多人遇人不淑係接二連三，鑊鑊識親都係仆街</blockquote><br />\n嗰啲叫 仆街攝石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但我努力改變梗自己 希望唔好再吸仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 而家都有拍拖 希望可以好似樓主咁幸幸福福<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係仆街磁石 唔係攝石<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b6f1a20cf43093b5f8700f840778d329c57627c","tid":89461,"uid":64869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:26:01.000Z","msg":"中間個男仔好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當佢水泡......"},{"pid":"d61e3b821227caba572f7124ff0dca81b02edb16","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T05:32:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>中間個男仔好撚慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你當佢水泡......</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以勸告大家唔好相信開始一段新戀情就可以忘記，唔好以為嘗試投入就會一日會愛佢，係唔會架。真係唔可行，真係會傷害到人，真係會後悔會自責。"},{"pid":"48643c9e52b4f84d6ce987b7c939d0c194d79870","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:11:26.000Z","msg":"個ex有乜咁吸引"},{"pid":"03be5604d6647989a4e3f66ee69229a439d32a7b","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:16:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>個ex有乜咁吸引</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n講真無，鍾意就係鍾意，無論佢個人有幾差，你都會好盲目，相信佢有一日會回心轉意。<br />\n<br />\n當唔再鍾意嘅時候，會發現當日有幾咁on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e6896f4cefc87264a39fa93b474ad2e8660cba75","tid":89461,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:20:44.000Z","msg":"咪撚扮哂野啦<br />\n賤女人玩弄女泡男"},{"pid":"744514e28435d6303a2755978a8b21c9bf22b991","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:31:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咪撚扮哂野啦<br />\n賤女人玩弄女泡男</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我絕對無玩佢，要講嘅就係咁多。"},{"pid":"80ac0574d7b0f2610ffba514fdb8e79f53aaa3fe","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:38:50.000Z","msg":"樓主依家幾歲?你現任溝到咁多女咁勁既"},{"pid":"542b9118e3e76014eaaab4bd6677c2bcbeedbf2c","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:41:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主依家幾歲?你現任溝到咁多女咁勁既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多歲就唔講啦，費事自爆，現任幾好樣，唔洗溝女，係女溝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02a35625bfe455ff0246eb3f4ad8ab5f7a33df81","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:43:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主依家幾歲?你現任溝到咁多女咁勁既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n幾多歲就唔講啦，費事自爆，現任幾好樣，唔洗溝女，係女溝佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n屈機啊"},{"pid":"7de8737b3bfab39e11ff91b4cf27bb3baa7354c9","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:43:40.000Z","msg":"樓主又拍過幾多次拖?"},{"pid":"e710e8651e301229b998749063ef25c5c7cfe608","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:45:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主又拍過幾多次拖?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上述個三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c0699f863ea7932676d11f2326c70a6bae8f38b","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:48:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>樓主又拍過幾多次拖?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上述個三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間個男仔有冇上過床?"},{"pid":"d6fe4b70ce8b606f6a2920ce46e3b518b1ba29d7","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T06:54:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>樓主又拍過幾多次拖?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n上述個三次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n中間個男仔有冇上過床?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n有。"},{"pid":"338d16b85d7d28c26c8aeb9f4f04f6ca38eca311","tid":89461,"uid":41602,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"得一句話比番樓豬<br />\n<br />\n比人傷害過，亦都傷害過人<br />\n<br />\n唔洗踏Ex抬自己既"},{"pid":"4cdec9ad5b0f845eaf97a2a6c38d40fd3648abfa","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:04:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>得一句話比番樓豬<br />\n<br />\n比人傷害過，亦都傷害過人<br />\n<br />\n唔洗踏Ex抬自己既</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果你有睇留言，我無抬高自己，多謝你。<br />\n比人傷害過，我覺得有所得著，<br />\n傷害過人我知道有嚟嘢係無法彌補，唔可以再犯。"},{"pid":"fb4c956fe0fa30e75efcff6a9d58474095b73ba5","tid":89461,"uid":9906,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:06:43.000Z","msg":"擦光所有火柴難令氣氛像從前閃耀<br />\n至少感激當日陪著我開甜蜜的玩笑"},{"pid":"c1ec4769fccc676339b879d1dd40bdffd9ebd7f0","tid":89461,"uid":37539,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:06:52.000Z","msg":"每個人係感情面前都會做仆街野，水泡男唔會蠢到連條女有去意都唔知。對方唔中意自己，灑脫一點更好。"},{"pid":"6c72d92b61c234abf7c27a85e5028a306acc4883","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:13:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擦光所有火柴難令氣氛像從前閃耀<br />\n至少感激當日陪著我開甜蜜的玩笑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"47a5285f9df4ec73ca26f8c62db9b381b151a300","tid":89461,"uid":58599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:17:50.000Z","msg":"分左手一個月 ，希望10年後同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7667a84366ff7c4eb4e7d5ffbb7814a4ea17c035","tid":89461,"uid":77106,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:18:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擦光所有火柴難令氣氛像從前閃耀<br />\n至少感激當日陪著我開甜蜜的玩笑</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6f90bed222a1969024776fe1ae7f24c37104cd","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>每個人係感情面前都會做仆街野，水泡男唔會蠢到連條女有去意都唔知。對方唔中意自己，灑脫一點更好。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個刹那係盲目嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"590d9bfc6e4e666d074d3ca2cfe619cc3f67f6d3","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:30:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>分左手一個月 ，希望10年後同樓主一樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你唔打10年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔會發現自己打錯標題，都無人發現我打錯標題，是但啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔洗10年咁耐嘅，千祈唔好同我一樣中途做錯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只要同我一樣最後得到幸福就夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc529915d28c4114e8c1443d61ac992acbf45343","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:39:00.000Z","msg":"女人係咪唔會介意現任屌過幾多條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要屌得你舒服就ok?"},{"pid":"5d6dc927ce315fa6a0416e954823545c53c04a71","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:40:51.000Z","msg":"其實去到尾都係講條件"},{"pid":"4b875dc41732315f2092a1e9665e6202bdadbfab","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:42:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人係咪唔會介意現任屌過幾多條女<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />只要屌得你舒服就ok?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n以前嘅事，點解要咁在意？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我個人就認為最重要係佢同我嘅感情，相處。<br />\n以前嘅事，已經過咗去。"},{"pid":"3a890d1b97f4d9ca197be459b0722ec489fac2fc","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T07:44:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實去到尾都係講條件</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟你充滿負能量喎，不如分享吓你嘅故事？"},{"pid":"f3c13d4b636ac732333ede0fc7c7d87920f30bf5","tid":89461,"uid":60561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T08:15:17.000Z","msg":"睇到水泡男嗰到，個心痛咗一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n襄王有夢，神女無心，做幾多都係把撚&hellip;<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n仲有，真正愛上一個人，邊會咁容易放得低<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"779d78858051804a584cf0b438ffa19f242f9765","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T09:17:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實去到尾都係講條件</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇嚟你充滿負能量喎，不如分享吓你嘅故事？</blockquote><br />\n只不過係好羨慕人地可以屌到咁多女姐，無咩故事分享"},{"pid":"3cf61d2abdc160d68b0e266e83bbcec0aa9086c4","tid":89461,"uid":31001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:23:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你怪人時有無諗過，水泡男其實都諗點解識到個咁仆街既女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好多謝佢喎，唔係佢，我唔知自己有乜唔好，可以去改進。唔係佢，我唔會識到現任。<br />\n<br />\n而被大家稱呼為水泡男嘅，我只能講係我錯，當初真係相信可以愛上佢，我好努力投入嚟段感情，但勉強真係做唔到，我有諗過我欠佢嘅，同佢行埋嚟下半世人都好應該，但我日日對住佢就諗住另一個真係好過分，所以去到差唔多半年嘅時候已經叫分手。<br />\n<br />\n但多次叫分手而佢挽留我話唔介意做水泡，我又無拒絕佢真係好錯，所以係最後我無理佢一個月唔再依賴佢，先至正式分手。<br />\n<br />\n希望佢唔好再咁傻，都唔好再遇到咁仆街嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72d6e275d0b933c3dfe274561e0ccaf5d1af4d4a","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:28:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>你怪人時有無諗過，水泡男其實都諗點解識到個咁仆街既女仔</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無怪人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我好多謝佢喎，唔係佢，我唔知自己有乜唔好，可以去改進。唔係佢，我唔會識到現任。<br />\n<br />\n而被大家稱呼為水泡男嘅，我只能講係我錯，當初真係相信可以愛上佢，我好努力投入嚟段感情，但勉強真係做唔到，我有諗過我欠佢嘅，同佢行埋嚟下半世人都好應該，但我日日對住佢就諗住另一個真係好過分，所以去到差唔多半年嘅時候已經叫分手。<br />\n<br />\n但多次叫分手而佢挽留我話唔介意做水泡，我又無拒絕佢真係好錯，所以係最後我無理佢一個月唔再依賴佢，先至正式分手。<br />\n<br />\n希望佢唔好再咁傻，都唔好再遇到咁仆街嘅女仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢好愛你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n錯愛，真係錯愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 寧願佢係個仆街"},{"pid":"cc6046245348020adaf8d53e9312eef237d928d5","tid":89461,"uid":16935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T10:41:05.000Z","msg":"認真你便輸了，食多d女好過"},{"pid":"0895fdc6d996acad2ea9aa6664930456d5d0ec52","tid":89461,"uid":482,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 只能說<br />\n我還沒準備好你出現了<br />\n等我準備好你也走了<br />\n<br />\n只能說錯的時間，對的人<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我真的很想親口講對唔住<br />\n但是我清楚知道你已經不想我在打擾<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2582e6d5debe14a3596b27fdaa90b94e3b6bf153","tid":89461,"uid":18695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T11:53:41.000Z","msg":"所以都係放低左前度<br />\n先好開始下一段關係<br />\n唔係既話 即使比你遇到好男人<br />\n但個心仍然係前度果度 <br />\n都唔會珍惜到眼前果位<br />\n更加唔好講愛佢<br />\n以為自己可以愛佢 忘記前度<br />\n基本上無咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後都係會分開<br />\n傷人又傷自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9e968ea7755c2d76e66a3d941ed08bcbb09d968","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:00:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>所以都係放低左前度<br />\n先好開始下一段關係<br />\n唔係既話 即使比你遇到好男人<br />\n但個心仍然係前度果度 <br />\n都唔會珍惜到眼前果位<br />\n更加唔好講愛佢<br />\n以為自己可以愛佢 忘記前度<br />\n基本上無咩可能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後都係會分開<br />\n傷人又傷自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係，放唔低真係無用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你明我表達乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n所以要好肯定自己放低咗先好再出發。<br />\n放低嘅過程會有難頂，但結果係美好就夠。"},{"pid":"28043525466d16341e91dd3831e430199be79fb8","tid":89461,"uid":38772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:06:43.000Z","msg":"臭系 水泡男都有個仆街ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到自己有幾慘咁 好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d5d1e0ad37bcfccfdc9038aadd1e7eefa542d7","tid":89461,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:12:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"57ad9de3005ae224b47e8e16d1146f0fb1b150a1","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:15:01.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>臭系 水泡男都有個仆街ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到自己有幾慘咁 好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無講自己好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔知你邊到睇到我講到自己好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是但啦，要講嘅我留言講曬，再重申一次我認我當時係仆街，我好自責，希望大家唔好相信開始一段新感情可以忘記舊嘅，我係一個人牌，完。"},{"pid":"678dedaa983308ce5ef03561062b41edadbd64d3","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:16:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>臭系 水泡男都有個仆街ex<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n講到自己有幾慘咁 好撚自私<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我無講自己好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 我唔知你邊到睇到我講到自己好慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 是但啦，要講嘅我留言講曬，再重申一次我認我當時係仆街，我好自責，希望大家唔好相信開始一段新感情可以忘記舊嘅，我係一個人<span style=\"color: red;\">版</span>，完。</blockquote>"},{"pid":"de75e5983cddb67ceaa944fc6cb4380920dc86b1","tid":89461,"uid":18568,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:21:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死臭西，含撚啦你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主係臭雞 製造弱者感覺<br />\n你同個第一個ex 一樣仆街"},{"pid":"b1d00c62974612049ba6affe7c8ac6fdf24e69d4","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:22:07.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>死臭西，含撚啦你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n去到邊都叫到你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又話返高登，幾時走？好行唔送"},{"pid":"c657a750066d031544ae66808ffd8913b977e36e","tid":89461,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:24:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6e066f50069d38845b30ffd241b01e01addf6c74","tid":89461,"uid":1254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:28:29.000Z","msg":"百日宴又去識仔！<br />\n好好傾呀？條仔第一次見你問你拎電話咪又係想呃蝦條<br />\n睇死你果陣都係想激你個ex所以先同人咁好傾<br />\n見到你扮豁達懶係放開咁就諗起欣宜啦<br />\n<br />\n然後又懶係後悔話對唔住個水泡仔<br />\n你知唔知其實你好撚令人作嘔？<br />\n收皮啦你"},{"pid":"da8998492829b664d9b1397f5deac955e4cd7060","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:29:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>死臭西，含撚啦你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n樓主係臭雞 製造弱者感覺<br />\n你同個第一個ex 一樣仆街</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你搞到我睇多次我打嘅嘢，介唔介意討論吓邊到製造弱者感覺，傾下，因為我自問完全無，我明明係嚟件事上面我認為自己係完全錯誤。<br />\n都想知係咪我當局者迷自我咗有啲嘢你get到我get唔到，講出嚟等我反思吓都好。<br />\n<br />\n我係仆街，但我同第一任ex係兩回事嘅仆街，唔同性質。"},{"pid":"930e93200101a9d3fd5a1f68d2f393b2df0357cb","tid":89461,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:31:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4e5501023631ddeeadfda2951ceef0f7916bea18","tid":89461,"uid":6631,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:31:59.000Z","msg":"其實樓主都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現任9個ex祝你好運"},{"pid":"b3ff0ac3ff4dbe552b2c4d64562abad924b15f08","tid":89461,"uid":34993,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"收啦屌"},{"pid":"c3fdbc0246528f91506d7df0da4056851957d8f0","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:36:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>百日宴又去識仔！<br />\n好好傾呀？條仔第一次見你問你拎電話咪又係想呃蝦條<br />\n睇死你果陣都係想激你個ex所以先同人咁好傾<br />\n見到你扮豁達懶係放開咁就諗起欣宜啦<br />\n<br />\n然後又懶係後悔話對唔住個水泡仔<br />\n你知唔知其實你好撚令人作嘔？<br />\n收皮啦你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咁嘅，係我問佢拎電話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你有參加過百日宴應該知道有好多枱，我坐最後，係無可能激到佢，主家人係坐最前嘅，順便一提我亦都無興趣咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而你點睇我真係影響唔到你，你作嘔你嘅事，我後悔我嘅事。"},{"pid":"70f495cb590a955f5e7fdf1275207a39ec493ae0","tid":89461,"uid":6869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:37:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"aa3adf64e2a33b7132c021c4c793e4fd9170c1d5","tid":89461,"uid":26320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:38:06.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實樓主都係仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n現任9個ex祝你好運</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係啊，我話咗我係。<br />\n人人故事不同，9個唔等於乜嘢嘅。"},{"pid":"12eb3fbad3386a0aaf8f3f8ea1dec108e42edb67","tid":89461,"uid":1254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-22T12:40:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>百日宴又去識仔！<br />\n好好傾呀？條仔第一次見你問你拎電話咪又係想呃蝦條<br />\n睇死你果陣都係想激你個ex所以先同人咁好傾<br />\n見到你扮豁達懶係放開咁就諗起欣宜啦<br />\n<br />\n然後又懶係後悔話對唔住個水泡仔<br />\n你知唔知其實你好撚令人作嘔？<br />\n收皮啦你</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n其實係咁嘅，係我問佢拎電話嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n如果你有參加過百日宴應該知道有好多枱，我坐最後，係無可能激到佢，主家人係坐最前嘅，順便一提我亦都無興趣咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而你點睇我真係影響唔到你，你作嘔你嘅事，我後悔我嘅事。</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n5個字<br />\n姣婆遇著脂粉客<br />\n講完"}]}